sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Dashboard
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant API as DS Pipelines API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTPS TLS(service-ca)
    participant DB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL TLS
    participant S3 as S3 Object Store<br/>443/9000 TCP HTTPS/HTTP
    participant PA as Persistence Agent
    participant SW as Scheduled Workflow
    participant WC as Workflow Controller<br/>(Argo)
    participant Envoy as MLMD Envoy<br/>9090/TCP HTTP
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>gRPC TLS

    Note over User,S3: Flow 1: Pipeline Submission and Execution

    User->>Router: POST /apis/v1beta1/pipelines<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS
    Router->>Proxy: Forward (Reencrypt TLS)<br/>8443/TCP
    Proxy->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA token
    K8sAPI-->>Proxy: Authorized
    Proxy->>API: Forward request<br/>HTTPS/8888, TLS(service-ca)
    API->>DB: Store pipeline metadata<br/>MySQL/3306, TLS(PodToPodTLS)
    API->>S3: Store pipeline artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, S3 credentials
    API->>K8sAPI: Create Workflow CR<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA token
    K8sAPI-->>API: Workflow created
    API-->>Proxy: Pipeline response
    Proxy-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>User: JSON Response

    Note over PA,K8sAPI: Flow 2: Pipeline Run Monitoring

    PA->>API: Poll run status<br/>HTTPS/8888, TLS(PodToPodTLS)
    PA->>K8sAPI: Watch Workflow status<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA token
    SW->>K8sAPI: Create scheduled Workflows<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA token

    Note over Envoy,MLMD: Flow 3: ML Metadata Access

    Note right of WC: Pipeline pods access MLMD
    WC->>Envoy: Store artifacts/executions<br/>HTTP/9090, gRPC-Web, plaintext
    Envoy->>MLMD: Forward gRPC<br/>gRPC, TLS(PodToPodTLS)
    MLMD->>DB: Persist metadata<br/>MySQL/3306, TLS(PodToPodTLS)
    DB-->>MLMD: Result
    MLMD-->>Envoy: Response
    Envoy-->>WC: Metadata stored
